parameters.query:
with ultima_pagina as (
  select max(pagina) as pagina from cor_beneficiario
)
select
  coalesce(u.pagina, 0) pagina,
  coalesce(count(c.id_beneficiario), 0) as total
from
  ultima_pagina u
  left join cor_beneficiario c on c.pagina = u.pagina
group by
  u.pagina;

select * 
from cor_pessoa p
where p.cpf_cnpj_pessoa = '{{ $('Loop Over Items1').item.json.associados.cpf }}'
order by p.dth_cad_pessoa desc
limit 1
